## Summary
This documentation page explains User Session Charts in Amplitude, which analyze user engagement patterns based on session metrics like session length distribution, average session duration, and sessions per user. It details how to build these charts, explains the different measurement options available (counting sessions vs events within sessions), and describes how Amplitude tracks sessions through server-side or client-side methods.

